DROP TABLE  if exists sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_06_1;					
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_06_1 stored as orc as					
select msisdn ani, tac, fecha, OS_parser, ver_num_parser, orden from (					
select a.msisdn,					
trim(substr(imei,1,8)) as tac,					
        fecha,
        b.version_parser_os OS_parser,
        b.version_parser_num ver_num_parser,
        row_number ()  over (partition by a.msisdn order by fecha desc) as orden					
    from trafico.huawei_dpi_consolidado a
    join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_user_agent_inter2 b on a.user_agent=b.user_agent
    where fecha between 20230501 and 20230504					
    and a.msisdn in (select ani from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_05)					
    and substr(imsi,1,3)=722
    and a.user_agent is not  null
    and a.user_agent <>''
    and a.user_agent <>'0'
    and tethering_flag=0
    )x where x.orden<=3;

DROP TABLE  if exists sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_010;					
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_010 stored as orc as					
select ani, fecha, tac,					
case when tac=tac_2 and tac=tac_3 then 1 else 0 end as fl_tac_valido,					
case when OS_parser=OS_parser_2 and OS_parser=OS_parser_3 then 1 else 0 end as fl_OS_parser_valido,	
case when ver_num_parser=ver_num_parser_2 and ver_num_parser=ver_num_parser_3 then 1 else 0 end as fl_ver_num_parser_valido,					
OS_parser,
ver_num_parser 
from(					
select 					
a.ani,					
a.fecha,					
a.tac,					
case when b.tac is null then a.tac else b.tac end as tac_2,					
case when c.tac is null then a.tac else c.tac end as tac_3,					
case when b.OS_parser is null then a.OS_parser else b.OS_parser end as OS_parser_2,					
case when c.OS_parser is null then a.OS_parser else c.OS_parser end as OS_parser_3,
case when b.ver_num_parser is null then a.ver_num_parser else b.ver_num_parser end as ver_num_parser_2,					
case when c.ver_num_parser is null then a.ver_num_parser else c.ver_num_parser end as ver_num_parser_3,
a.OS_parser,
a.ver_num_parser 
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_09 a					
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_09 b on a.ani=b.ani and b.orden=2					
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_09 c on a.ani=c.ani and c.orden=3					
where a.orden=1					
)x;

as					
select

from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_14 a					
left join 					
(

from

y.version_final,					
row_number ()  over (partition by y.modelo_final order by y.Q desc) as rnk

DROP TABLE  if exists sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_16;					
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_16 stored as orc as					
select 					
ani,					
mes_parque,					
segmento,					
producto,					
cei_mes,					
fecha_so,					
tac,					
marca,					
regexp_replace(modelo, ',', '') as modelo,					
nombre_modelo,					
--version_base_terminal,					
--version_tope_terminal,					
--gama,					
--fecha_primera_homologacion,					
version_final,					
cast(version_num as string) version_num,					
cast(version_mayoritaria as string) version_mayoritaria,					
CASE WHEN marca LIKE '%Apple Inc%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS fl_apple,
CASE WHEN marca NOT LIKE '%Apple Inc%' 
        AND version_final NOT LIKE '%iOS%' 
        AND CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(version_num, '.', 1) AS INT) < 10 
        AND version_num IS NOT NULL 
        AND CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(version_num, '.', 1) AS INT) < CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(version_mayoritaria, '.', 1) AS INT) 
     THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS fl_actualizable_android,
CASE WHEN marca NOT LIKE '%Apple Inc%' 
        AND version_final NOT LIKE '%iOS%' 
        AND version_num IS NOT NULL 
        AND CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(version_num, '.', 1) AS INT) < 5 
     THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS fl_cater_android,
CASE WHEN marca LIKE '%Apple Inc%' 
        AND version_final LIKE '%iOS%' 
        AND CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(version_num, '.', 1) AS DECIMAL) < CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(version_mayoritaria, '.', 1) AS DECIMAL) 
     THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS fl_actualizable_apple,
CASE WHEN marca LIKE '%Apple Inc%' 
        AND version_final LIKE '%iOS%' 
        AND CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(version_num, '.', 2) AS FLOAT) < 14.6
     THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS fl_actualizable_apple_ultimo_update,				
case when modelo in  ('Apple iPhone 5C (A1516)',					
'Apple iPhone 5C (A1526)',					
'Apple iPhone 5S (A118)',					
'Apple iPhone 5S (A1518)',					
'Apple iPhone 5S (A1528)',					
'Apple iPhone 5C (A1529)',					
'Apple iPhone 5C (A1456)',					
'Apple iPhone 5C (A1532)',					
'Apple iPhone 5C (A1507)',					
'Apple iPhone 5 (A1429)',					
'Apple iPhone 5S (A1530)',					
'Apple iPhone 5S (A1453)',					
'Apple iPhone 5S (A1533)',					
'Apple iPhone 5S (A1457)',					
'Apple iPhone 4S (A1387)',					
'Apple iPhone S (A1530)'					
) then 1 else 0 end as fl_cater_apple					
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_15;

DROP TABLE  IF EXISTS sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_android_tmp;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_android_tmp stored AS orc AS
SELECT 
    a.*,
    CASE 
        WHEN (CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL) < 4 AND a.fl_actualizable_android = 1) THEN 'cater'
        WHEN (CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL) = 4 AND a.fl_actualizable_android = 1) THEN 'actualizacion'
        WHEN a.fl_cater_android = 1 THEN 'cater'
        ELSE 'actualizacion'
    END AS fl_caso
FROM sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_16 a
WHERE a.fl_apple = 0
    AND (a.fl_actualizable_android = 1 OR a.fl_cater_android = 1)
    AND (CAST(SPLIT(a.version_mayoritaria, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL)) < 11.00
    AND (
        (CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL) < 8 AND 
        CAST(version_mayoritaria AS DECIMAL) - CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL) <= 3)
        OR CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL) >= 8
    );

DROP TABLE  IF EXISTS sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_parque_tmp;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_equipos_actualizables_parque_tmp stored AS orc AS

SELECT a.*, 
CASE 
    WHEN a.fl_apple = 1 AND a.fl_cater_apple = 1 THEN 'Obsoleto'
    WHEN a.fl_apple = 1 AND a.version_final LIKE '%iOS%' AND CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS INT) < 10 THEN 'Obsoleto'
    WHEN a.fl_apple = 1 AND a.version_final LIKE '%iOS%' AND CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL) >= 13.40 THEN 'Maximo:(>=8 Android o >=13.4 Apple)'
    WHEN a.fl_apple = 1 AND a.version_final LIKE '%iOS%' AND CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS DECIMAL) < 13.40 AND CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS INT) >= 10 THEN 'Medio: (Entre 5 y 7 Android / Entre 10 y 13.4 Apple)'
    WHEN a.fl_apple = 0 AND CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS INT) < 5 THEN 'Obsoleto'
    WHEN a.fl_apple = 0 AND a.fl_cater_android = 1 THEN 'Obsoleto'
    WHEN a.fl_apple = 0 AND a.version_final NOT LIKE '%iOS%' AND CAST(SPLIT(a.version_num, '\\.')[0] AS INT) >= 8 THEN 'Maximo:(>=8 Android o >=13.4 Apple)'
